---

Notes

- Each model is executed independently
- Preprocessing must be completed before running models
- All models use shared evaluation logic from `Metrics.py`

---

Troubleshooting

- Ensure dependencies are installed correctly
- Verify dataset is placed inside the `archive` folder
- Confirm correct script execution order
- Use Python 3.13 for best compatibility

